uel_et_collectif/pistolet_automatique_pamas_g1 |title=Pistolet automatique PAMAS G1 |language=fr |publisher=Defense.gouv.fr |date=2011-12-13 |accessdate=2012-03-04 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100619130640/http://www.defense.gouv.fr/terre/decouverte/materiels/armement_individuel_et_collectif/pistolet_automatique_pamas_g1 |archivedate=2010-06-19 }}</ref><ref name=\"marchington2004\">Marchington, James (2004). ''The Encyclopedia of Handheld Weapons''. Lewis International, Inc. {{ISBN|1-930983-14-X}}.</ref><ref>{{cite web|language=fr|title=PAMAS G1|url=http://gendarmes.net/default_zone/fr/html/page336.html|publisher=gendarmes.net/|accessdate=29 September 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005043926/http://gendarmes.net/default_zone/fr/html/page336.html|archive-date=5 October 2016|url-status=live}}.</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagu|Georgia}}\n|[[Georgian Police]]\n| align=\"center\"|Yavuz 16\n| align=\"center\"|_\n| align=\"center\"|_\n| align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"girsan\"/>\n|-\n| {{flagu|India}}\n| [[Mizoram Armed Police]], [[MARCOS]] \n| align=\"center\"| 92S\n| align=\"center\"| \n| align=\"center\"|\n| align=\"center\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sinlung.com/2010/09/mizoram-police-to-get-latest-weapons.html |title=Mizoram Police to Get Latest Weapons |publisher=Sinlung |date=2010-09-14 |accessdate=2012-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311141229/http://www.sinlung.com/2010/09/mizoram-police-to-get-latest-weapons.html |archive-date=2012-03-11 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|{{flag|Indonesia}}\n| ''[[Kopassus|Komando Pasukan Khusus]]'' (Kopassus) special forces group of the [[Indonesian Army]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"|_\n|align=\"center\"| _\n|align=\"center\"| _\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"idnvojnik\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hrvatski-vojnik.hr/hrvatski-vojnik/1612007/ind.asp |title=Kopassus & Kopaska \u2013 Specijalne Postrojbe Republike Indonezije |language=Croatian |