f>\n|-\n| {{flagu|Jordan}}\n| [[Jordanian Armed Forces]] (JAF) \n| align=\"center\"|M9\n| align=\"center\"| _\n| align=\"center\"| _\n| align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"diez2000\"/>\n|-\n| {{flagu|Kuwait}}\n| \n| align=\"center\"| _\n| align=\"center\"| _\n| align=\"center\"| _\n| align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Thompson2011\">{{cite book|author=Leroy Thompson|title=The Beretta M9 Pistol|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YVbDCwAAQBAJ&pg=PT88|date=20 September 2011|publisher=Bloomsbury Publishing|isbn=978-1-84908-837-4|pages=88\u2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagu|Luxembourg}}\n| ''[[Unit\u00e9 Sp\u00e9ciale de la Police]]'' of the [[Grand Ducal Police]]\n| align=\"center\"| 92F\n| align=\"center\"|\n| align=\"center\"|_\n| align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Unofficial\">{{cite web|url=http://www.usp.lu/armement-pistolets-fr.php|title=Unofficial Pistols Page, Equipment|publisher=USP.lu \u2013 Unofficial Website of Unit\u00e9 Sp\u00e9ciale, Officially Endorsed|accessdate=2009-10-06|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722161231/http://www.usp.lu/armement-pistolets-fr.php|archivedate=2011-07-22}}</ref><ref name=\"RAIDS\">{{cite web |url=http://www.usp.lu/media/raids.pdf |title=L'Unite d'Intervention de la Police Luxembourgeoise |year=2006 |language=French |publisher=RAIDS Magazine |accessdate=2009-09-23 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722160041/http://www.usp.lu/media/raids.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-22 }}</ref><ref name=\"ARMAS\">{{cite web |url=http://www.usp.lu/media/armas.pdf |title=UPS Unidad Especial de la Policia Luxembourguesa |author=Lasterra, Juan Pablo |year=2004 |language=Spanish |publisher=ARMAS Magazine |accessdate=2009-09-23 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722161849/http://www.usp.lu/media/armas.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-22 }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagu|Libya}}\n| [[Libyan National Army]] (LNA) \n| align=\"center\"|M9\n| align=\"center\"| _\n| align=\"center\"| _\n| align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"diez2000\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |{{flagu|Malaysia}}\n| [[10 Paratrooper Brigade (Malaysia)|10 Paratrooper Brigade]]  rapid deployment forces of the [[Malaysian Army]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"|92FS\n| align=\"center\"|\n| align=\"center\"|\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite book|title=Malaysia Army Weapon Systems Handbook|author=IBP USA |pages=71\u201373|publisher= Int'l Business Publication|year=2007 |ISBN= 978-1-4330-6180-6}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Grup Gerak Khas]]'' special forces of the [[Malaysian Army]]\n| align=\"center\"| \n| align=\"center\"| _\n|-\n| [[Malaysian Road Transport Department]]\n| align=\"center\"| 92 Compact L\n| align=\"center\"| _\n| align=\"center\"| _\n| align=\"center\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://219.95.62.14/etraining/takwim/calendar.php?com=calendar&task=detail&id=88 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714151200/http://219.95.62.14/etraining/takwim/calendar.php?com=calendar&task=detail&id=88 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2014-07-14 |title=Situation Shooting Course Series 3/2010 |author=Malaysian Road Transport Academy |language=Malay |accessdate=2009-10-06 }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagu|Malta}}\n|[[Armed Forces of Malta]]\n| align=\"center\"|92FS\n| align=\"center\"|\n| align=\"center\"|\n| align=\"center\"| <ref>{{cite news|title=Personnel reveal shortcomings inside Maltese armed forces|url=https://www.maltatoday.com.mt/news/national/88089/personnel_reveal_shortcomings_inside_maltese_armed_forces|newspaper=[[Malta Today]]|date=14 July 2018|first=Matthew|last=Agius|access-date=26 April 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422132901/https://www.maltatoday.com.mt/news/national/88089/personnel_reveal_shortcomings_inside_maltese_armed_forces|archive-date=22 April 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagu|Mexico}}\n|Various branches of the armed forces\n| align=\"center\"| _\n| align=\"center\"|\n| align=\"center\"|_\n| align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"jones2009\"/>\n|-\n| {{flagu|Monaco}}\n|''[[Compagnie des C