al_code            =\n|area_code              =\n|blank_name             =\n|blank_info             =\n|website                =\n|footnotes              = \n}}\n\n'''Rampurwa ''' is a [[Village development committee (Nepal)|village development committee]] in [[Nawalparasi District]] in the [[Lumbini Zone]] of southern [[Nepal]]. At the time of the [[1991 Nepal census]] it had a population of 3689 people living in 542 individual households.<ref>{{Cite web| url=http://www.digitalhimalaya.com/collections/nepalcensus/form.php?selection=1|title=Nepal Census 2001|work=Nepal's Village Development Committees|publisher=[[Digital Himalaya]]|accessdate=18 December 2008 }}</ref>\n\n==References==\n<references />\n\n{{Nawalparasi district data}}\n\n{{coord|29|13|N|80|58|E|source:plwiki|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Parasi District]]\n\n{{Province5NP-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Pegship", "label": "safe", "comment": "update district", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rampurwa,_Parasi"}
{"title_page": "Falkenau", "text_new": "{{for|the town in Bohemia|Sokolov, Czech Republic}}\n{{Infobox German location\n|type = Ortsteil\n|Town = Fl\u00f6ha\n|name              = Falkenau\n|image_photo       = Falkenau as seen from north-west (aka).jpg\n|image_caption     = Falkenau\n|image_coa            = Wappen Falkenau.png\n|coordinates       = {{coord|50|51|19|N|13|6|57|E|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n|state        = Sachsen\n|district         = Mittelsachsen\n|elevation              = 321\n|area            = 9.08\n|population         = 2040\n|Stand             = 2006-12-31\n|postal_code               = 09557\n|area_code           = 03726\n|licence               = FG\n|Adresse           = Stra\u00dfe der Einheit 26<br />09557 Falkenau\n|website           = [http://www.gemeinde-falkenau.de www.gemeinde-falkenau.de]\n}}\n\n'''Falkenau''' is a village and a former municipality in the district of [[Mittelsachsen]], in [[Saxony]], [[Germany]]. Since 1 October 2011, it is part of the town [[Fl\u00f6ha]].\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Saxony]]\n[[Category:Fl\u00f6ha]]\n[[Category:Bezirk Karl-Marx-Stadt]]\n\n\n{{Mittelsachsen-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{for|the town in Bohemia|Sokolov, Czech Republic}}\n{{Infobox German location\n|type = Ortsteil\n|Town = Fl\u00f6ha\n|name              = Falkenau\n|image_photo       = Falkenau as seen from north-west (aka).jpg\n|image_caption     = Falkenau\n|image_coa            = Wappen Falkenau.png\n|coordinates       = {{coord|50|51|19|N|13|6|57|E|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n|state        = Sachsen\n|district         = Mittelsachsen\n|elevation              = 321\n|area            = 9.08\n|population         = 2040\n|Stand             = 2006-12-31\n|postal_code               = 09557\n|area_code           = 03726\n|licence               = FG\n|Adresse           = Stra\u00dfe der Einheit 26<br />09557 Falkenau\n|website           = [http://www.gemeinde-falkenau.de 