{"title_page": "Eutzsch", "text_new": "{{Infobox German location\n|type = Stadtteil\n|Town = [[Kemberg]]\n|image_photo       = \n|image_coa            = kein\n|coordinates       = {{coord|51|49|N|12|38|E|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n|image_plan          = \n|state        = Sachsen-Anhalt\n|district         = Wittenberg\n|elevation              = 67\n|area            = 13.83\n|population         = 654\n|Stand             = 2006-12-31\n|postal_code               = 06888\n|area_code           = 03491\n|licence               = WB\n|divisions        = 3 \n|Adresse-Verband   = Burgstra\u00dfe 5<br />06901 Kemberg\n|website           = [https://web.archive.org/web/20070927231035/http://www.vwg-kemberg.de/p/dl1.asp?artikel_id=&liste=213&tmpl_typ=Liste&lp=1014 www.vgem-kemberg.de]\n}}\n\n'''Eutzsch''' is a village and a former municipality in [[Wittenberg (district)|Wittenberg]] district in Saxony-Anhalt, [[Germany]]. Since 1 January 2010, it is part of the town [[Kemberg]].\n\n== Geography ==\nEutzsch lies about 6&nbsp;km south of [[Lutherstadt Wittenberg]].\n\n== History ==\nEutzsch had its first documentary mention in 965 under the name ''Usizi''.\n\n== Politics ==\nThe municipal council is made up of 10 councillors.\n\n== Economy and transportation==\nFederal Highway (''Bundesstra\u00dfe'') B 2 between Wittenberg and [[Bad D\u00fcben]], and the B 100 both run straight through the community. Eutzsch's [[railway station]] is on the [[Railway|line]] running from [[Berlin]] to [[Nuremberg]] and [[Munich]].\n\n== External links ==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20060118070112/http://www.vwg-kemberg.de/ Administrative community's website]\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Saxony-Anhalt]]\n[[Category:Bezirk Halle]]\n\n\n{{Wittenberg-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox German location\n|type = Stadtteil\n|Town = [[Kemberg]]\n|image_photo       = \n|image_coa            = kein\n|coordinates       = {{coord|51|49|N|12|38|E|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n|image_plan          = \n|state        = Sachsen-Anhalt\n|district         = Wittenberg\n|elevation              = 67\n|area            = 13.83\n|population         = 654\n|Stand             = 2006-12-31\n|postal_code               = 06888\n|area_code           = 03491\n|licence               = WB\n|divisions        = 3 \n|Adresse-Verband   = Burgstra\u00dfe 5<br />06901 Kemberg\n|website           = [https://web.archive.org/web/20070927231035/http://www.vwg-kemberg.de/p/dl1.asp?artikel_id=&liste=213&tmpl_typ=Liste&lp=1014 www.vgem-kemberg.de]\n}}\n\n'''Eutzsch''' is a village and a former municipality in [[Wittenberg (district)|Wittenberg]] district in Saxony-Anhalt, [[Germany]]. Since 1 January 2010, it is part of the town [[Kemberg]].\n\n== Geography ==\nEutzsch lies about 6&nbsp;km south of [[Lutherstadt Wittenberg]].\n\n== History ==\nEutzsch had its first documentary mention in 965 under the name ''Usizi''.\n\n== Politics ==\nThe municipal council is made up of 10 councillors.\n\n== Economy and transportation==\nFederal Highway (''Bundesstra\u00dfe'') B 2 between Wittenberg and [[Bad D\u00fcben]], and the B 100 both run straight through the community. Eutzsch's [[railway station]] is on the [[Railway|line]] running from [[Berlin]] to [[Nuremberg]] and [[Munich]].\n\n== External links ==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20060118070112/http://www.vwg-kemberg.de/ Administrative community's website]\n\n[[Category:Villages in Saxony-Anhalt]]\n[[Category:Bezirk Halle]]\n\n{{Wittenberg-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eutzsch"}
