i District|Fengtai]]\n|305.53 ||2,112,162 ||2,098,632 ||[[Fengtai Subdistrict]] ||100000 ||16 ||2 ||3 ||254 ||73\n|-\n! 110107 !! {{nowrap|[[Shijingshan District|Shijingshan]]}}\n|84.38 || colspan=\"2\" |616,083 ||[[Lugu Subdistrict, Beijing|Lugu Subdistrict]] ||100000 ||9 ||style=\"background:gray;\"|&nbsp;||style=\"background:gray;\"|&nbsp;||130 ||style=\"background:gray;\"|&nbsp;\n|-\n! 110108 !! [[Haidian District|Haidian]]\n|430.77 ||3,280,670 ||3,208,563 ||[[Haidian Subdistrict]] ||100000 ||22 ||7 ||style=\"background:gray;\"|&nbsp;||603 ||84\n|-\n! 110109 !! [[Mentougou District|Mentougou]]\n|1447.85 ||290,476 ||248,547 ||[[Dayu Subdistrict]] ||102300 ||4 ||9 ||style=\"background:gray;\"|&nbsp;||124 ||179\n|-\n! 110111 !! [[Fangshan District|Fangshan]]\n|1994.73 ||944,832 ||635,282 ||[[Gongchen Subdistrict]] ||102400 ||8 ||14 ||6 ||108 ||462\n|-\n! 110112 !! [[Tongzhou District, Beijing|Tongzhou]]\n|905.79 ||1,184,256 ||724,228 ||[[Beiyuan Subdistrict, Beijing|Beiyuan Subdistrict]] ||101100 ||6 ||10 ||1 ||40 ||480\n|-\n! 110113 !! [[Shunyi District|Shunyi]]\n|1019.51 ||876,620 ||471,459 ||[[Shengli Subdistrict, Beijing|Shengli Subdistrict]] ||101300 ||6 ||19 ||style=\"background:gray;\"|&nbsp;||61 ||449\n|-\n! 110114 !! [[Changping District|Changping]]\n|1342.47 ||1,660,501 ||1,310,617 ||[[Chengbei Subdistrict, Beijing|Chengbei Subdistrict]] ||102200 ||8 ||14 ||style=\"background:gray;\"|&nbsp;||180 ||303\n|-\n! 110115 !! [[Daxing District|Daxing]]\n|1036.34 ||1,365,112 ||965,683 ||[[Xingfeng Subdistrict]] ||102600 ||5 ||14 ||style=\"background:gray;\"|&nbsp;||64 ||547\n|-\n! 110116 !! [[Huairou District|Huairou]]\n|2122.82 ||372,887 ||253,088 ||[[Longshan Subdistrict, Beijing|Longshan Subdistrict]] ||101400 ||2 ||12 ||2 ||27 ||286\n|-\n! 110117 !! [[Pinggu District|Pinggu]]\n|948.24 ||415,958 ||219,850 ||[[Binhe Subdistrict, Beijing|Binhe Subdistrict]] ||101200 ||2 ||14 ||2 ||23 ||275\n|-\n! 110118 !! [[Miyun District|Miyun]]\n|2225.92 ||467,680 ||257,449 ||