ook of Contemporary China|url=https://archive.org/details/cambridgehandboo0000mack|url-access=registration|quote=beiping beijing.|place=Cambridge|publisher=[[Cambridge University Press]]|isbn=978-0-521-38755-2|accessdate=22 July 2009|ref=harv}}\n{{refend}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Sister project links|voy=Beijing|Beijing}}\n* [http://info.hktdc.com/mktprof/china/mpbei.htm Economic profile for Beijing] at [[Hong Kong Trade Development Council|HKTDC]]\n* [https://www.facebook.com/BeijingChinaOfficial Visit Beijing Facebook Page]\n* [http://cudl.lib.cam.ac.uk/view/PH-Y-00302-E/4 Photograph of ''The approach to Peking \u2013 outside the walls''] taken in 1890 by [[Sir Henry Norman, 1st Baronet|Sir Henry Norman]]\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Hangzhou|Lin'an]] ([[Song dynasty]])|row=1}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Historical capitals of China|Capital of China]] (as [[Khanbaliq|Dadu]] of [[Yuan dynasty|Yuan]])\n|years=1264\u20131368|row=1}}\n{{S-aft|after=[[Nanjing]] ([[Ming dynasty]])|row=1}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Nanjing]] ([[Ming dynasty]])|row=2}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Historical capitals of China|Capital of China]]\n|years=1420\u20131928|row=2}}\n{{S-aft|after=[[Nanjing]] ([[Republic of China|ROC]])|row=2}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Nanjing]] ([[Republic of China|ROC]]) |row=3}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Historical capitals of China|Capital of the People's Republic of China]]\n|years=1949\u2013present|row=3}}\n{{S-aft|after=present capital|row=3}}\n{{S-end}}\n{{Beijing}}\n{{Geographic location\n|Centre = Beijing\n|North =\n|Northeast = [[Chengde]], Hebei\n|East = [[Langfang]], Hebei\n|Southeast = [[Tianjin]]\n|South = [[Langfang]], Hebei\n|Southwest = [[Baoding]], Hebei\n|West =\n|Northwest = [[Zhangjiakou]], Hebei\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Articles related to Beijing\n|list =\n{{Province-level divisions of the People's Republic of China}}\n{{Metropolitan cities of the People's Republic of China}}\n{{Most populous cities in the People's Republic of China}}\n{{List of Asian capitals by region}}\n{{Museums in Beijing}}\n{{Olympic Summer Games Host Cities}}\n{{Paralympic Summer Games Host Cities}}\n{{Olympic Winter Games Host Cities}}\n{{Paralympic Winter Games Host Cities}}\n{{Asian Games Host Cities}}\n{{IAAF World Championships in Athletics Host cities}}\n{{World's most populated urban areas}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Beijing| ]]<!--please leave the empty space as standard-->\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Capitals in Asia]]\n[[Category:Metropolitan areas of China]]\n[[Category:North China Plain]]\n", "name_user": "SS49", "label": "safe", "comment": "date formats perMOS:DATEFORMATbyscript", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beijing"}
